{"AT":[{"def":"Primarily, this word expresses the relations of presence, nearness in place or time, or direction toward; as, at the ninth hour; at the house; to aim at a mark.","pos":""}],"AT ONE":[{"def":"In concord or friendship; in agreement (with each other); as, to be, bring, make, or set, at one, i.","pos":""},{"def":"Of the same opinion; agreed; as, on these points we are at one.","pos":""}]}